//! The TML Standard Library.
//!
//! This library provides common functionality for TML programs, including
//! collections, I/O, networking, string manipulation, and error handling.
//!
//! # Modules
//!
//! | Module | Description |
//! |--------|-------------|
//! | [`traits`] | Core behaviors (Copy, Eq, Ord, Hash) |
//! | [`oop`] | OOP support (interfaces, Object base class) |
//! | [`interfaces`] | Re-export of `oop::interfaces` (backward compat) |
//! | [`object`] | Re-export of `oop::object` (backward compat) |
//! | [`exception`] | Exception class hierarchy |
//! | [`types`] | Free-standing helpers for Maybe[T], Outcome[T, E] |
//! | [`collections`] | List, HashMap, Buffer, ArrayList, BTreeMap, etc. |
//! | [`text`] | Dynamic string type |
//! | [`file`] | File I/O operations |
//! | [`iter`] | Iterator and Range |
//! | [`net`] | Networking (TCP, UDP, HTTP) |
//! | [`json`] | Native JSON parsing |
//! | [`sync`] | Synchronization primitives (Mutex, Arc, atomics) |
//! | [`thread`] | Threading utilities (scoped threads, thread-local) |
//! | [`crypto`] | Cryptography (SHA, AES, RSA, ECDH, X.509, KDF) |
//! | [`hash`] | Fast non-crypto hashes (FNV-1a, Murmur2) for ETags |
//! | [`zlib`] | Compression (gzip, deflate, brotli, zstd) |
//! | [`log`] | Structured logging with level-based filtering |
//! | [`os`] | Operating system information and utilities |
//! | [`search`] | Vector search and text retrieval (BM25, HNSW, SIMD) |
//! | [`glob`] | High-performance glob pattern matching |
//! | [`math`] | Mathematical functions and constants |
//! | [`time`] | Time measurement (Instant, sleep) |
//! | [`random`] | Pseudo-random number generation |
//! | [`datetime`] | UTC date and time from Unix timestamps |
//! | [`alloc`] | Specialized allocators (Arena, Pool, Cache, SOO) |
//! | [`io`] | I/O error types (IoError, IoErrorKind) |

